race.comment: HAMPE (3) Shaft gelding from a Bel Esprit mare on debut for the Peter Morgan yard. Has impressed in both trials and gets every chance from the inside gate. FORTE CHEVAL (2) returns from a let-up after coming back in trip when third over 1000m at Corowa. Proven on his home track from the good gate. YES MAXI (7) made an encouraging debut from the awkward gate when a game third over 1180m at Gundagai. Improver who can overcome the draw. Respect. BRILLIANT BEAGLE (9) never in contention from the barrier when a struggling seventh over 1000m at Tatura. Looking for this trip and worth thought. HAZ STYLES (4) has finally drawn a decent gate and desperate for this trip. Will roll forward and give plenty of cheek.
